" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">Calcul automatique des frais basé sur les services</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">Traitement et jugement des réclamations d&#x27;assurance</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">Facturation patient avec relevés détaillés</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-slate-600">Traitement des paiements en ligne avec plusieurs options</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-5 w-5 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5